    MissingValue,
    MissingVariantKey,
    MissingLiteral,
    MultipleDefaultVariants,
    MessageReferenceAsSelector,
    TermReferenceAsSelector,
    MessageAttributeAsSelector,
    TermAttributeAsPlaceable,
    UnterminatedStringExpression,
